sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App
    participant NotificationService
    participant ChatService

    User->>App: Enable push notifications
    App->>NotificationService: Register for notifications
    NotificationService-->>App: Confirmation

    User->>App: Send a new message
    App->>ChatService: Deliver message
    ChatService-->>App: Message delivered

    App->>NotificationService: Send push notification for new message
    NotificationService-->>User: Push notification received

    User->>App: Adjust notification settings for chat
    App->>NotificationService: Update notification preferences
    NotificationService-->>App: Preferences updated

    User->>App: Disable push notifications for specific chat
    App->>NotificationService: Update notification settings
    NotificationService-->>App: Settings updated